metadata.name: VERD & MORJANIO
metadata.description: In a land called Fantasiato, there is a magical realm full of wonderful creatures with fantastic faces. Each creature has a face that represents their special abilities and personalities. Verd, with a green head adorned with multiple eyes, has the gift of foresight that allows him to perceive hidden wonders. Morjanio, with a head decorated with moving purple tentacles, has the ability to bring life to inanimate objects. Together they discover the secrets of fantasy and live in the fabric of their strange world.
